;*************************************************************************
;** Optimizes short loops of the '010 for LoopMode			**
;** Contributor: Jess Sosnoski         			Jul 4th   1998  **
;** replaces subq.w #1,d0 - loops by dbra				**
;*************************************************************************

#match
#code
%0101001101000XXX	=# SourceReg	;subq.w #1,dx
64FA					;bhs (to above)
#replace
%0101000111001XXX	=# SourceReg	;dbra dx (to above)
FFFC
#end
